  m_text: 'At approximately 11:40 PM, an accident occurred in a small private garage
    workshop located on the outskirts of the city.


    The worker on duty, Ramesh
    Patel, was found unconscious on the floor by a colleague arriving for the morning
    shift. There were no witnesses, and the workshop was left in a disordered and
    hazardous state.


    Your role is to:


    Investigate the environment, identify
    safety violations, and determine the cause of the accident.'
